    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short cloaks covering the shoulders and designed to be worn at night, as is required by some religious orders. Such scapulars may be of various designs; an example is joined by bands at the side and has the hood attached to it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
